title: NCAA Division I Football Stadiums w/ Capacities, USA, 2007
name: NCAA Division I Football Stadiums w/ Capacities, USA, 2007
description: Did you know that 19 of the 20 largest stadiums in the U.S. belong to universities? Given the large number of people who crowd into these stadiums, knowing their locations and the capacities is useful not only to sports fans, but to anyone interested in risk analysis.                                                 This information was collected from Wikipedia http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_stadiums_by_capacity and universities' athletics websites.                                                 The stadiums were mapped by their latitude and longitude coordinates.Note: Some universities are listed twice because they play home games at two stadiums.
